   <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aici, drume</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17">t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ul nu mai este con</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ş</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">tient de sine, nici de lucrurile din jurul lui. Nu vede nici ignoran</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ţ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">a, nici cunoa</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ş</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">terea, nici îndoiala, nici certitudinea; nu face deosebire între diminea</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ţ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">a c</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ă</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">l</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ă</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">uzirii </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17">s</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i noaptea erorii. El fuge atât de necredin</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ţ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ă</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1"> cât </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ş</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i de credin</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ţ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ă</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17">s</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i pentru el otrava este un balsam; a</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ş</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">a precum ‘A</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"> t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T30">.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"> t</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T30">.</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">ár</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Footnote_20_Characters"><text:span text:style-name="T1"><text:note text:id="ftn11" text:note-class="foo